{"title_page": "Sahil Khattar", "text_new": "{{Infobox YouTube personality\n|name=Sahil Khattar\n|birth_date=21 March 1991\n|birth_place=\n|nationality=Indian\n|occupation=Youtuber, actor, television host\n|website= \n|channel_display_name=Khattarnaak\n|channel_display_name2=Being Indian\n|channel_direct_url=channel/UCJvcAis0LDFkLXrKOOjrXgw\n|channel_direct_url2=channel/UChAlpEbfW1y9auiBC08ZwGQ\n|views=364,108,806\n|view_date=26 February 2020\n|silver_button=yes\n|gold_button=yes\n|stats_update = 26 February 2020\n}}\n'''Sahil Khattar''' (born 21 March 1987) is an Indian YouTuber, television host and actor.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://article.wn.com/view/2018/04/28/Sahil_Khattar_turns_Mission_Commander_for_The_Expedition/|title=Sahil Khattar turns Mission Commander for The Expedition|website=article.wn.com|publisher=[[World News Network]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/events/sahil-khattar-i-want-france-to-win-the-football-world-cup-this-time/articleshow/64998403.cms|title=Sahil Khattar: I want France to win the Football World Cup this time - Times of India|publisher=[[The Times of India]]|access-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180902061326/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/life-style/events/sahil-khattar-i-want-france-to-win-the-football-world-cup-this-time/articleshow/64998403.cms|archive-date=2018-09-02|url-status=live|df=}}</ref> He works with two YouTube channels, named ''Khattarnaak'' and ''Being Indian''. In 2007, he became a [[radio jockey]]<ref name=\"HT\"/> and then joined the content creation company Being Indian. He then moved to mainstream TV with hosting television shows like [[Dance India Dance]],<ref>{{cite news |title=After hosting Dance India Dance S6, YouTube sensation Sahil Khattar eyes Bollywood |url=https://www.indiatvnews.com/entertainment/celebrities-after-hosting-dance-india-dance-s6-youtube-sensation-sahil-khattar-eyes-bollywood-448014 |date=18 June 2018}}</ref> [[India's Raw Star]] and [[India's Got Talent]].{{citation needed|date=January 2019}}\n\n== Career==\nKhattar started his career as a radio jockey along with writing scripts for various acts. He became popular doing YouTube videos for Being Indian and also hosted television show Dance India Dance.<ref>{{cite news |title=Dance India Dance: Sahil Khattar, Amruta Khanvilkar launch sixth season of reality show |url=https://www.firstpost.com/photos/dance-india-dance-sahil-khattar-amruta-khanvilkar-launch-sixth-season-of-reality-show-4187645.html |work=www.firstpost.com}}</ref> He is also a sports enthusiast and has hosted sports events like [[Football World Cup 2018|Russia World Cup 2018]] on [[Sony Ten#Sony Ten 3|Sony Ten 3]] and live [[cricket]] show, India tour of England on [[Sony Liv]].\n\nHe  claims that actress [[Priyanka Chopra]]<ref>{{cite news |title=Sahil Khattar: I had no work in 2014; Priyanka Chopra gave me a chance  to write for an event |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/sahil-khattar-i-had-no-work-in-2014-priyanka-chopra-gave-me-a-chance-to-write-for-an-event/story-KSkCKleGQ7kJUrmistUWTM.html |work=Hindustan Times |date=29 November 2017 |language=en |access-date=2018-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121043207/http://www.hindustantimes.com/tv/sahil-khattar-i-had-no-work-in-2014-priyanka-chopra-gave-me-a-chance-to-write-for-an-event/story-KSkCKleGQ7kJUrmistUWTM.html |archive-date=2018-01-21 |url-status=live |df= }}</ref> was the one which gave him an opportunity to write while he was hosting India\u2019s Raw Star. \nHe wrote for [[Shah Rukh Khan|Shahrukh Khan]], [[Salman Khan]], [[Mukesh Ambani]] and  [[Nita Ambani]] until he decided to say those lines by himself and move to YouTube and Television.\n\nHis latest show is ''The Expedition''<ref>{{cite news |title=Sahil Khattar turns Mission Commander for The Expedition |url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/sahil-khattar-turns-mission-commander-for-the-expedition/19367189 |work= Mid-Day |date=27 April 2018 |language=en}}</ref> on [[Zing (TV channel)|Zing]].\n\nHe is also playing Sayed Kirmani <ref name=\"HT\">{{cite news |last1=DelhiFebruary 1 |first1=India Today Web Desk New |last2=February 1 |first2=India Today Web Desk New |last3=Ist |first3=India Today Web Desk New |title=YouTuber Sahil Khattar to play Syed Kirmani in Ranveer Singh-starrer 83 |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/youtuber-sahil-khattar-to-play-syed-kirmani-in-ranveer-singh-starrer-83-1444439-2019-02-01 |work=India Today |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title='83': Ranveer Singh introduces Sahil Khattar as wicketkeeper Syed Kirmani - Times of India |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/83-ranveer-singh-introduces-sahil-khattar-as-wicketkeeper-syed-kirmani/articleshow/73372922.cms |work=The Times of India |language=en}}</ref>in [[Kabir Khan (director)|Kabir Khan]]'s 83 which is based of Indian Cricket team winning the 1983 world cup. This movie also starers [[Ranveer Singh]], [[Deepika Padukone]]\n\n\n\n== Awards ==\n*\"Top 30 Under 30\" ''(For Sahil\u2019s energy and constant passion for work)''<ref>{{cite news |title=From RJ to YouTube star, Sahil Khattar among Top 30 Under 30: \u2018My energy is my X factor\u2019 |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/sahil-khattar-among-top-30-under-30-at-ht-youth-forum-2017/story-jJjt6OWpwjisEAspcVJC9K.html |work=Hindustan Times |date=24 May 2017 |language=en |access-date=2018-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180109061849/http://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/sahil-khattar-among-top-30-under-30-at-ht-youth-forum-2017/story-jJjt6OWpwjisEAspcVJC9K.html |archive-date=2018-01-09 |url-status=live |df= }}</ref> presented by ''[[Hindustan Times]]''.\n*India\u2019s Top 10 Super Stars,<ref>{{cite news |title=Meet India's top 10 YouTube superstars - Meet India's YouTube superstars |url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/people/meet-indias-top-10-youtube-superstars/sahil-khattar/slideshow/52173570.cms |work=The Economic Times |access-date=2018-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012175228/http://economictimes.indiatimes.com/slideshows/people/meet-indias-top-10-youtube-superstars/sahil-khattar/slideshow/52173570.cms |archive-date=2017-10-12 |url-status=live |df= }}</ref> by ''[[The Economic Times]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/sahil-khattar-on-paleo-diet-for-the-expedition-118052400138_1.html|title=Sahil Khattar on Paleo diet for 'The Expedition'|first=|last=IANS|date=24 May 2018|publisher=|via=Business Standard|access-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524062815/http://www.business-standard.com/article/news-ians/sahil-khattar-on-paleo-diet-for-the-expedition-118052400138_1.html|archive-date=2018-05-24|url-status=live|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.freepressjournal.in/entertainment/sahil-khattar-feels-overwhelmed/1167525|title=Sahil Khattar feels overwhelmed   - Free Press Journal|date=9 November 2017|publisher=|access-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180121112001/http://www.freepressjournal.in/entertainment/sahil-khattar-feels-overwhelmed/1167525|archive-date=2018-01-21|url-status=live|df=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/sahil-khattar-on-paleo-diet-for-the-expedition/19455197|title=Sahil Khattar on Paleo diet for The Expedition|date=24 May 2018|publisher=}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dnaindia.com/television/report-being-indian-face-sahil-khatter-to-now-host-a-tv-show-2513662|title='Being Indian' face Sahil Khattar to now host a TV show|date=26 July 2017|publisher=|access-date=2018-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170727174706/http://www.dnaindia.com/television/report-being-indian-face-sahil-khatter-to-now-host-a-tv-show-2513662|archive-date=2017-07-27|url-status=live|df=}}</ref>\n\n== Filmography ==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Rol