-i-had-no-work-in-2014-priyanka-chopra-gave-me-a-chance-to-write-for-an-event/story-KSkCKleGQ7kJUrmistUWTM.html |archive-date=2018-01-21 |url-status=live |df= }}</ref> was the one which gave him an opportunity to write while he was hosting India\u2019s Raw Star. \nHe wrote for [[Shah Rukh Khan|Shahrukh Khan]], [[Salman Khan]], [[Mukesh Ambani]] and  [[Nita Ambani]] until he decided to say those lines by himself and move to YouTube and Television.\n\nHis latest show is ''The Expedition''<ref>{{cite news |title=Sahil Khattar turns Mission Commander for The Expedition |url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/sahil-khattar-turns-mission-commander-for-the-expedition/19367189 |work= Mid-Day |date=27 April 2018 |language=en}}</ref> on [[Zing (TV channel)|Zing]].\n\nHe is also playing Sayed Kirmani <ref name=\"HT\">{{cite news |last1=DelhiFebruary 1 |first1=India Today Web Desk New |last2=February 1 |first2=India Today Web Desk New |last3=Ist |first3=India Today Web Desk New |title=YouTuber Sahil Khattar to play Syed Kirmani in Ranveer Singh-starrer 83 |url=https://www.indiatoday.in/movies/bollywood/story/youtuber-sahil-khattar-to-play-syed-kirmani-in-ranveer-singh-starrer-83-1444439-2019-02-01 |work=India Today |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title='83': Ranveer Singh introduces Sahil Khattar as wicketkeeper Syed Kirmani - Times of India |url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/hindi/bollywood/news/83-ranveer-singh-introduces-sahil-khattar-as-wicketkeeper-syed-kirmani/articleshow/73372922.cms |work=The Times of India |language=en}}</ref>in [[Kabir Khan]]'s 83 which is based of Indian Cricket team winning the 1983 world cup. This movie also starers [[Ranveer Singh]], [[Deepika Padukone]]\n\n\n\n== Awards ==\n*\"Top 30 Under 30\" ''(For Sahil\u2019s energy and constant passion for work)''<ref>{{cite news |title=From RJ to YouTube star, Sahil Khattar among Top 30 Under 30: \u2018My energy is my X factor\u2019 |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/punjab/sahil-k